data.description: Location, location, location! Discover the charm of this delightful single-level home in Millett Ranch just in front of the Community Park! With 3 beds, 2 baths, & a thoughtfully designed floorplan, this property maximizes its square footage. The 2-car garage w/attached cabinetry is just the beginning. Enter to find a perfectly flowing living & dining room paired with vaulted ceilings & wood laminate flooring, creating an inviting & open space. The kitchen boasts black SS appliances, honey oak cabinetry, a pantry, & a pass-through window. Split main bedroom has a full bathroom w/a walk-in closet. Washer & dryer included. The entertainer's backyard awaits with covered & open patios, a grassy area, & a sparkling pool as a centerpiece. This gem is move-in ready. Welcome home!
